Columbine students returned to classes at Chatfield High School on Monday.
Monday, Columbine and Chatfield senior high schools came together yet again, neither as rivals nor as mourners, but as partners in helping Columbine students to reclaim their lives as normal teenagers for whom school is a place to learn, not to flee.
It was a columbine, a perennial that will bloom again this month.Columbine Students Return to School Students of the Columbine High School in Colorado State of the United States finally returned to class Monday after two weeks of school closure due to the campus shooting tragedy.
